"сторонниками:"

#. type: Content of: <appendix><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/credits.xml:21
msgid ""
"Robert Kehl, who created the Win32-installer for the 1.x releases. Thanks a "
"lot, Robert!"
msgstr ""
"Robert Kehl, создавший Win32-инсталлятор для релиза 1.x. Больше тебе "
"спасибо, Robert!"

#. type: Content of: <appendix><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/credits.xml:26
msgid ""
"Torsten Werner, who maintains the Debian-installer for OTRS. Thanks a lot, "
"Torsten, by making OTRS also available for the Debian community."
msgstr ""
"Torsten Werner, который поддерживаетм Debian-installer для OTRS. Спасибо "
"большое, Torsten, теперь OTRS также доступен для Debian-сообщества."

#. type: Content of: <appendix><para><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/credits.xml:31
msgid ""
"Nils Jeppe (mirror Hamburg, Germany), Bryan Fullerton (mirror Toronto, "
"Canada), Eberhard Mönkeberg (mirror Göttingen, Germany), Timo Dreger (mirror "
"Düsseldorf, Germany) and Netmonic (mirror Vienna, Austria), who are "
"mirroring our FTP server. Thanks a lot, with your help it is always possible "
"to download OTRS quickly!"
msgstr ""
"Nils Jeppe (зеркало Гамбург, Германия), Bryan Fullerton (зеркало Торонто, "
